items.name: Avengers (2010) #1 (I AM AN AVENGER BLANK COVER VARIANT)

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #1
results.description: Determined to keep the tradition alive, founding Avenger Hank Pym leads a core team of veteran heroes in creating a place where the next generation of Earth's Mightiest can be trained by the greatest of those who preceded them.

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #10
results.description: It's a day in the life of the students at the Avengers Academy when special guest instructors Protector and Dr. Strange arrive. The lesson quickly ends as a powerful villain resurfaces, forcing student and teacher to assemble together.

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #11
results.description: With no intention to go with her husband, Carina enlists the aid of the Avengers to fight on her behalf. When Korvac defeats some of Earth's mightiest heroes, however any hope of survival depends on Avengers Academy!

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #12
results.description: Accepting Carina's offer to grant the teens the powers of their future incarnations, the students of the Avengers Academy square off against Korvac! Will the power boost of the future be enough to stop him, and what will it mean for the present?

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #2
results.description: Hank Pym, Quicksilver, Tigra, Justice and Speedball are here to mentor the next generation of Earth's Mightiest Heroes...but is one of the students hot for teacher? Plus: Get a glimpse inside the mind of Finesse!

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #3
results.description: SCARED STRAIGHT PART 1 The Academy kids are sent to The Raft to be scared straight by the all-new Thunderbolts. But things go from scary to downright insane when the Academy students are locked inside with Norman Osborn!

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #4
results.description: SCARED STRAIGHT PART 2 The crossover with the Thunderbolts rages on! There's a jailbreak at The Raft, the maximum security prison for super villains, and the students of Avengers Academy are caught in the middle! But whose side are they on?

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #5
results.description: Obsessed super-criminal Whirlwind blames Hank Pym for the death of the woman he loved, Janet Van Dyne, and comes seeking revenge on Hank's inexperienced students, who are out on a field trip!

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #6
results.description: Reptil goes Jurassic on Tigra! As he struggles with the weight of his repressed grief and anger, something's got to give...and it might just be Reptil's humanity! Plus: more on Quicksilver and Finesse, the villainy of Mentallo, and another Avengers guest appearance!

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #7
results.description: After an unfortunate accident, the Absorbing Man is released from custody and runs rampant on the city! With no options left, the students of the Avengers Academy must assemble against a foe that even their teachers cannot defeat. Fly or flunk!

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #8
results.description: After the students of the Avengers Academy discover that one of Tigra's most fearsome enemies has escaped from prison, the teens seek out vengeance. Will this be the team's first steps towards being heroes or will they give in to more villainous ways?

results.title: Avengers Academy (2010) #9
results.description: After recent events at the Academy, Finesse steps-out to find her father. Tracking down Taskmaster, she intends to see if her roots lie in crime. Has what she learned at school prepared her for a battle of brain and brawn?

results.title: Avengers Academy #9
results.description: Guest-starring Taskmaster! As the fallout from Tigra's shocking act last issue rocks the Academy, Finesse goes in search of the man who could be her father...the character readers have demanded since issue #1...Taskmaster! Be here for the explosive reunion in the book that IGN.com calls â€œthe best Avenger book on the market.â€
